From 033dbe4238b09990bdc30c1c93b234dcb1e90019 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pengfei Zhang <penzhan@qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 25 May 2026 22:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ath12k: add CFR support

Port ath12k CFR (Channel Frequency Response) support from ath11k.
Adds CFR capture infrastructure including debugfs interface, WMI
commands, and DMA ring handling.

Upstream-Status: Pending
Signed-off-by: Penzhan <penzhan@qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/Kconfig       |  11 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/Makefile      |   1 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/cfr.c         | 990 ++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/cfr.h         | 297 ++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.c        |  12 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.h        |  17 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dbring.c      |  18 +-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dbring.h      |   6 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/debug.h       |   2 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/debugfs_sta.c | 167 +++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.h          |   3 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c         |  15 +-
 .../wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_wcn7850.c   |   2 +-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c    |   4 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wmi.c         | 151 ++-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wmi.h         |  87 +-
